      <title>彩虹雨后的蘑菇城堡 —— 发现与惊喜</title>
      <link>https://blog.jaxiu.cn/blog/2026-03/%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E9%9B%A8%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1-%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%8E%E6%83%8A%E5%96%9C/</link>
